Motioneyeos
https://github.com/ccrisan/motioneyeos/wiki/Wifi-Preconfiguration
Extract the image to your hard drive
Write the image to your microSD card
DO NOT EJECT THE SD CARD yet.
Create wpa_supplicant.conf in the top directory
Make sure you set the EOL conversion to UNIX LineFeeds
Paste the following contents into your blank file (obviously changing the ssid and psk to match yours):
        country=US
        update_config=1
        ctrl_interface=/var/run/wpa_supplicant
        
        network={
            scan_ssid=1
            ssid="MyWiFiSSID"
            psk="S3cr3tp@$$w0rc|"
        }
